      <title>德国民粹主义浪潮威胁国家气候行动势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/germany-s-populist-surge-puts-nation-s-climate-momentum-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，德国东部两个州的选举中民粹主义高涨，发出信号表明，对旨在清理欧洲最大经济体的政策的反对声音正在日益高涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/germany-s-populist-surge-puts-nation-s-climate-momentum-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 12:28:39 GMT</pubDate>
