      <title>中菲争端引发南海新冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/china-philippines-row-opens-new-flashpoint-in-south-china-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在中菲两国刚刚达成缓解南海热点地区紧张局势的协议后不久，两国船只近日发生的冲突又引发了南海新的冲突爆发点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/china-philippines-row-opens-new-flashpoint-in-south-china-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 10:28:04 GMT</pubDate>
