      <title>土耳其竞相加入金砖国家，力争建立超越西方的联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/turkey-submits-bid-to-join-brics-as-erdogan-pushes-for-new-alliances-beyond-west</link>
